{"tid":2477601,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有個女手足就嚟生日！！","createTime":"2021-04-06T12:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-06T16:31:03.000Z","uid":238696,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3d3126072c23f6cc13ee81cd857c6ab5b6172469","tid":2477601,"uid":238696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"【為鄭手足送上生日祝福】<br />\n<br />\n鄭手足已還押逾1個月，今個月尾她將在獄中渡過生日。石牆花在此呼籲有心人為她來寫生日信，歡迎大家寄生日信件給這位手足，將溫暖送到她的手中🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n為免信件延誤，請在4月16日前把信件寄至石牆花。<br />\n<br />\n地址：九龍荔枝角青山道485號九龍廣場11樓01室<br />\n<br />\n***由於懲教署對卡類（生日卡/節日卡等）有數量限制，敬請大家不要寄生日卡過來，石牆花只會轉寄生日信，感謝！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV2oACj6CVmpukscvWM6s6f4RcsUVe4ybi4FKpCxsSzAf?filename=dOvDkV4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdOvDkV4.jpg&h=de1c24f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44280be8e696a7c788b6dba10cbce97147dbf201","tid":2477601,"uid":191661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">推！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 